{"tid":1365232,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"（睡前學習系列）《只差一隻》","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:07:59.000Z","uid":64232,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"04e26c1700d5911182d2b77b497942f402ea55d4","tid":1365232,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"從前，有一隻狼衝入羊群，羊們大亂，死傷慘重。<br />\n<br />\n有些羊拼死反抗，齊咬着狼的前足、後足，並呼籲更多羊們來抵抗。<br />\n<br />\n「差我一個不多，我們天生根本就不夠狼鬥。」後面的羊都這樣說。<br />\n<br />\n就這樣，前面的羊不斷反抗，後面大亂的繼續大亂。<br />\n<br />\n狼殺到最後，才說：「幸好你們沒有反抗，其實只要有一次，一同有五隻羊反抗，封我四肢，再咬中我的喉嚨，我就死定了。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，那時候只餘下四隻羊了。"},{"pid":"3e37db602539cff572a6d931fb0dfb17fb71f50d","tid":1365232,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c447507ba205ec99bbd3ed06ba8ad6e604ec8454","tid":1365232,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2f17426e942349d136865651a5e649b4f9d8dc","tid":1365232,"uid":90818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"留名，一直有睇樓主你既短文，好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f24566911675df52364b3e3e27d56889a9b9e9","tid":1365232,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"和理非留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861ca5ee17a38be61809d0b595fed912212f0b58","tid":1365232,"uid":225869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d42776d324759da71faa34f1de13bdcfde5be1","tid":1365232,"uid":2015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9cb1ea4d9938109220510f7fc05d46577c4c6c45","tid":1365232,"uid":242767,"like":0,"